{
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  },
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "links": [],
  "liveNow": false,
  "refresh": "10s",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": ["im", "microservices", "observability"],
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Prometheus",
        "multi": false,
        "name": "datasource",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "regex": "",
        "type": "datasource"
      },
      {
        "allValue": ".*",
        "current": { "text": "All", "value": "$__all" },
        "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
        "definition": "label_values(im_db_query_duration_ms_count, service_name)",
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": true,
        "label": "Service",
        "multi": true,
        "name": "service",
        "options": [],
        "query": {
          "qryType": 1,
          "query": "label_values(im_db_query_duration_ms_count, service_name)",
          "refId": "PrometheusVariableQueryEditor-VariableQuery"
        },
        "refresh": 2,
        "regex": "",
        "sort": 1,
        "type": "query"
      }
    ]
  },
  "time": { "from": "now-1h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "IM — Microservices Observability",
  "uid": "im-microservices-obs",
  "version": 1,
  "weekStart": "",
  "panels": [
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Database — im_db_query_duration_ms (wired, all services hit the DB)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "id": 100,
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "DB queries / sec (by service)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 1 },
      "id": 1,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 12, "showPoints": "never", "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(im_db_query_duration_ms_count{service_name=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "DB query latency p50 / p95 / p99 (ms)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 1 },
      "id": 2,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 8, "showPoints": "never", "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "ms",
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum by (le) (rate(im_db_query_duration_ms_bucket{service_name=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p50",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(im_db_query_duration_ms_bucket{service_name=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p95",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum by (le) (rate(im_db_query_duration_ms_bucket{service_name=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "p99",
          "refId": "C"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total DB queries / sec",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 9 },
      "id": 3,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "reqps", "color": { "mode": "thresholds" }, "thresholds": { "mode": "absolute", "steps": [{ "color": "green", "value": null }] } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area", "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(im_db_query_duration_ms_count{service_name=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "DB avg query latency (ms) by service",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 18, "x": 6, "y": 9 },
      "id": 4,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 8, "showPoints": "never", "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "ms",
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(im_db_query_duration_ms_sum{service_name=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])) / sum by (service_name) (rate(im_db_query_duration_ms_count{service_name=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "row",
      "title": "HTTP server — OTel auto-instrumentation",
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 17 },
      "id": 101,
      "collapsed": false,
      "panels": []
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "HTTP requests / sec (by service)",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 18 },
      "id": 5,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 12, "showPoints": "never", "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "reqps",
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["mean", "max"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (service_name) (rate(http_server_duration_milliseconds_count{service_name=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "HTTP latency p95 (ms) by service",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 18 },
      "id": 6,
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 8, "showPoints": "never", "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "ms",
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "calcs": ["max"] }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le, service_name) (rate(http_server_duration_milliseconds_bucket{service_name=~\"$service\"}[$__rate_interval])))",
          "legendFormat": "{{service_name}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Notes",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 26 },
      "id": 7,
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Data sources used here:** `im_db_query_duration_ms` (custom, wired in shared-db) + OTel auto HTTP metrics.\n\n- If the **DB panels** are empty, the metric pipeline itself isn't reaching Grafana — check `OBSERVABILITY_ENABLED` and the OTLP metric exporter (in Explore, search `im_db_query_duration_ms_count`).\n- If the **HTTP panels** are empty, your build exports the newer semconv name — change `http_server_duration_milliseconds_*` to `http_server_request_duration_seconds_*` (and unit ms→s).\n- If the **Service** dropdown is empty, your setup labels the service as `job` instead of `service_name` — replace `service_name` with `job` throughout.\n- **WebSocket / messages / fanout** panels need `im_ws_*` / `im_messages_*` / `im_message_fanout_*` to be recorded in realtime-service first (currently defined but not called)."
      }
    }
  ]
}
